name: ePestSolutions
overview:
ePestSolutions is the do-it yourself pest control firm offering an array of the most proficient pest control products and supplies used by industry specialists, for use in the home market. With an expertise of over 20 years, they are able to provide the best treatment to one’s pest problems in the most cost effective way by adhering to the ‘Do-it Yourself’ approach. Besides, its team of expert entomologist provides advice and support along with a video that guides about the entire process, to consumers who have any kind of enquiries and doubts. It also renders a special line of organic pest control products registered by EPA.

It offers solutions to all kinds of pest problems with a multitude of pest control products including animal traps, ant controls, fly traps, earwig insecticides and granules, pantry pest traps and bait, fungus and mold treatment, rodent control kits, flea control kits and spray scorpion insecticide, termite control and bait, cricket insecticides and bait, fly traps and glue boards, etc. Its solutions are available in concentrated formulas in both liquid and powder formulations. Its fast shipping services enable consumers to have quick access to these products after their order.
